ar Distinguished Service Medal]]\n* [[Image:Texas Outstanding Service Medal Ribbon.svg|80px]] [[Texas Outstanding Service Medal]]\n* [[File:USA - TX Medal of Merit Service Ribbon.png|80px]] [[Texas Medal of Merit]] (also awarded with \"V\" for valor)\n* [[File:Cold War Victory Medal ribbon.svg|80px]]  Texas [[Cold War Victory Medal]]\n* [[File:USA - TX Adjunct Generals Award.jpg|80px]] [[Texas Adjutant General's Individual Award]]\n* [[Image:Texas Federal Service Medal Ribbon.svg|80px]] [[Texas Federal Service Medal]]\n* [[Image:Texas Desert Shield-Desert Storm Campaign Medal Ribbon.svg|80px]] [[Texas Desert Shield-Desert Storm Campaign Medal]]\n* [[Image:Texas Humanitarian Service Ribbon.svg|80px]] [[Texas Humanitarian Service Ribbon]]\n* [[Image:Texas Homeland Defense Service Ribbon.svg|80px]]  [[Texas Homeland Defense Service Medal]]\n* [[File:USA - TX Combat Service Ribbon.png|80px]] [[Texas Combat Service Ribbon]]\n* [[File:USA - TX Cavalry Service Medal Service Ribbon.png|80px]] [[Texas Cavalry Service Medal]]\n* [[Image:Texas Faithful Service Medal Ribbon.svg|80px]] [[Texas Faithful Service Medal]]\n* [[File:USA - TX State Guard Association Service Ribbon.png|80px]] Texas State Guard Association Service Ribbon\n* [[File:USA - TX State Commanding General's Individual Award Ribbon.png|80px]] Texas State Commanding General's Individual Award Ribbon\n* [[File:USA - TX State Guard Enlisted Personnel Basic Training Ribbon.png|80px]] Texas State Guard Enlisted Personnel Basic Training Ribbon\n* [[File:USA - TX State Guard NCO Professional Development Service Ribbon.png|80px]] Texas State Guard NCO Professional Development Service Ribbon\n* [[File:USA - TX State Guard Officer Professional Development Service Ribbon.png|80px]] Texas State Guard Officer Professional Development Service Ribbon\n* [[File:USA - TX State Guard Meritorious Service ribbon.png|80px]] Texas State Guard Meritorious Service Ribbon\n* [[File:USA - TX State Guard Recruiting Service Ribbon.png|80px