ibbon\n\n== [[Vermont]] ==\n'''Vermont National Guard State Awards:'''\n\n* [[File:Vermont Distinguished Service Medal State Award.jpg|80px]] Vermont Distinguished Service Medal (National Guard award)\n* [[File:Vermont Medal for Merit.JPG|80px]] Vermont Medal of Merit\n* [[File:Vermont Commendation Medal.JPG|80px]] Vermont Commendation Medal\n* [[File:Meritorious Service Ribbon.JPG|80px]] Vermont Meritorious Service Ribbon\n* [[File:Outstanding Unit Award.JPG|80px]] Vermont Outstanding Unit Award\n* [[File:Organizational Excellence Award.JPG|80px]] Vermont Organizational Excellence Award\n* [[File:World War II Medal.jpg|80px]] Vermont World War II Medal\n* [[File:Vt National Defense Service Medal.JPG|80px]] Vermont National Defense Medal\n* [[File:Good Conduct Ribbon.JPG|80px]] Vermont Good Conduct Ribbon\n* [[File:Desert Strom Ribbon.JPG|80px]] Vermont Desert Storm Ribbon\n* [[File:Albtr.png|80px]] Vermont Active Duty for Training Ribbon\n* [[File:Professional Development Medal.JPG|80px]] Vermont Professional Development Ribbon\n* [[File:Career Service Award.JPG|80px]] Vermont Career Service Award\n* [[File:PA 20YM.JPG|80px]] Vermont Service Ribbon\n* [[File:Duty Ribbon.JPG|80px]] Vermont Duty Ribbon\n* [[File:State Special Duty Ribbon.JPG|80px]] Vermont State Special Duty Ribbon\n* [[File:Noribbon.svg|80px]] Vermont Military Humanitarian Service Medal\n\n'''Related:'''\n* [[File:Vermont Patriots Medal.JPG|80px]] [[Vermont Patriots Medal]]\n* [[File:Vt Distinguished Service Medal.JPG|80px]] [[Vermont Distinguished Service Medal]] (Veterans award)\n* [[File:Vermont Veterans Medal Ribbon (3).jpg|80px]] [[Vermont Veterans Medal]]\n\n== [[U.S. Virgin Islands|Virgin Islands]] ==\nVirgin Islands National Guard Territory Awards\n\n* [[File:VI NG Distinguished Service Medal.PNG|80px]] Virgin Islands Distinguished Service Medal\n* [[File:VI Meritorious Service Medal.JPG|80px]] Virgin Islands Meritorious Service Medal\n* [[File:VI National Guard Commendation Medal.JPG|80px]]