13 August 2015 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc from the village of Sochy}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://latarnia-morska.eu/pl/port-literacki/906-qwidok-na-ycieq-teresy-ferenc |title=Teresa Ferenc \"Widok na \u017cycie\", Towarzystwo Przyjaci\u00f3\u0142 Sopotu, Sopot 2012, str. 64 |access-date=14 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc \"Widok na \u017bycie\", Society of Friends of Sopot, Sopot 2012, p. 64}}</ref>\n* ''Stara jak \u015bwiat'' (\"Old as the world\") (2004),<ref>{{cite web |url=http://mkidn.gov.pl/pages/posts/wiceminister-sellin-wreczyl-odznaczenia-6633.php |title=Wiceminister Sellin wr\u0119czy\u0142 odznaczenia |date=3 October 2016 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Deputy Minister Sellin presented awards}}</ref>\n* ''Ogniopis. Wyb\u00f3r wierszy'' (\"Ogniopis. Selection of poems\") (2009),<ref>{{cite web |url=http://latarnia-morska.eu/pl/port-literacki/906-qwidok-na-ycieq-teresy-ferenc |title=Teresa Ferenc \"Widok na \u017cycie\", Towarzystwo Przyjaci\u00f3\u0142 Sopotu, Sopot 2012, str. 64 |access-date=14 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc \"Widok na \u017bycie\", Society of Friends of Sopot, Sopot 2012, p. 64}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://mkidn.gov.pl/pages/posts/wiceminister-sellin-wreczyl-odznaczenia-6633.php |title=Wiceminister Sellin wr\u0119czy\u0142 odznaczenia |date=3 October 2016 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Deputy Minister Sellin presented awards}}</ref>\n* ''Widok na \u017cycie'' (\"A view of life\") (2012)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://latarnia-morska.eu/pl/port-literacki/906-qwidok-na-ycieq-teresy-ferenc |title=Teresa Ferenc \"Widok na \u017cycie\", Towarzystwo Przyjaci\u00f3\u0142 Sopotu, Sopot 2012, str. 64 |access-date=14 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc \"Widok na \u017bycie\", Society of Friends of Sopot, Sopot 2012, p. 64}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://mkidn.gov.pl/pages/posts/wiceminister-sellin-wreczyl-odznaczenia-6633.php |title=Wiceminister Sellin wr\u0119czy\u0142 odznaczenia |date=3 October 2016 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Deputy Minister Sellin presented awards}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.worldcat.org/search?q=au%3AFerenc%2C+Teresa.&qt=hot_author |title=World Cat. Ferenc Teresa |access-date=14 February 2020 |language=English |trans-title=World Cat. Ferenc Teresa}}</ref>\n* ''Wiersze. Wybor'' (\"Poems. Choice\") (2017)<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.amazon.com/Wiersze-Wybor/dp/8364708252 |title=\"Wiersze. Wybor.\" Ferenc Teresa |access-date=14 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=\"Poems. Choice.\" Ferenc Teresa}}</ref>\n\n==Characteristics of creativity==\nIn his poetry, he touches on topics related to love, corporeality and motherhood. In her poetry she also often returns to the tragedy of her childhood - in 1943, as a nine-year-old child, she witnessed how almost all residents (including her [[parents]]) were shot by the [[Germans]]; the village itself was then bombed and burned (hence the fire motif returns in its poetry).<ref>{{cite book |last=Kuncewicz |first=Piotr |date=1995 |title=Leksykon polskich pisarzy wsp\u00f3\u0142czesnych |trans-title=Lexicon of Polish contemporary writers |language=pl |location=Warsaw |publisher=Graf-Punkt |isbn=83-86091-29-0}}, p. 219.</ref><ref>{{cite book |last=Borkowska |first=Gra\u017cyna |last2=Czermi\u0144ska |first2=Ma\u0142gorzata |last3=Philips |first3=Ursula |date=2000 |title=Pisarki polskie od \u015bredniowiecza do wsp\u00f3\u0142czesno\u015bci |trans-title=Polish writers from the Middle Ages to the present day |language=Polish |location=Gda\u0144sk |publisher=S\u0142owo Obraz Terytoria |isbn=83-87316-74-1}}</ref>\n\nTeresa Ferenc wrote in poem ''Wie\u015b skamienia\u0142a'' (poem: \"The village is petrified\") about the [[Sochy massacre]], which she survived in her childhood:<br />\"June 1, 1943 on the edge of the [[Zwierzyniec]] forests\nmy village was shot.<br />[[Sochy, Lublin Voivodeship|Sochy]] - like in [[Oradour-sur-Glane massacre|Oradour]] in [[France]],<br />Sochy - like in [[Lidice massacre|Lidice]] in [[Czech Republic]],<br />Sochy - like in [[Sant'Anna di Stazzema massacre|Mezzinote]] in [[Italy]].\"<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.kurierzamojski.pl/teresa-ferenc-ze-wsi-sochy/ |title=Teresa Ferenc ze wsi Sochy |last=Ciurysek |first=Agnieszka |date=13 August 2015 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc from the village of Sochy}}, ''Wie\u015b skamienia\u0142a'' (poem: \"The village is petrified\")</ref>\n\n==Selected awards and nominations==\n* 1979 - Nagroda im. Stanis\u0142awa Pi\u0119taka (''Gda\u0144ska Ksi\u0105\u017cka Roku 1979'' w dziedzinie poezji) za tom poezji ''Wypalona dolina'' (\"The prize Stanis\u0142aw Pi\u0119tak ('' Gda\u0144sk Book of the Year 1979 '' in the field of poetry) for the poetry volume \"Burned Valley\"\")<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.kurierzamojski.pl/teresa-ferenc-ze-wsi-sochy/ |title=Teresa Ferenc ze wsi Sochy |last=Ciurysek |first=Agnieszka |date=13 August 2015 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc from the village of Sochy}}</ref>\n* 1997 - wyr\u00f3\u017cnienie przyznane przez Fundacj\u0119 Kultury za ''Bo\u017ce pole'' (\"distinction awarded by the Culture Foundation for \"God's field\"\")<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.kurierzamojski.pl/teresa-ferenc-ze-wsi-sochy/ |title=Teresa Ferenc ze wsi Sochy |last=Ciurysek |first=Agnieszka |date=13 August 2015 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc from the village of Sochy}}</ref>\n* 1997 - nagroda ''Media Ksi\u0105\u017cce'' (''Gda\u0144ska Ksi\u0105\u017cka Wiosny'') za ''Bo\u017ce pole'' (\"''Media Book'' award (''Gda\u0144sk Spring Book'') for \"God's field\"\")<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.kurierzamojski.pl/teresa-ferenc-ze-wsi-sochy/ |title=Teresa Ferenc ze wsi Sochy |last=Ciurysek |first=Agnieszka |date=13 August 2015 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc from the village of Sochy}}</ref>\n* 2004 - ''Nagroda Artusa 2004'' za zbi\u00f3r ''Stara jak \u015bwiat'' (\"\"Artus Award 2004\" for the collection \"Old as the World\"\")<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.kurierzamojski.pl/teresa-ferenc-ze-wsi-sochy/ |title=Teresa Ferenc ze wsi Sochy |last=Ciurysek |first=Agnieszka |date=13 August 2015 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc from the village of Sochy}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://wiadomosci.onet.pl/gdanska-ksiazka-roku-2004/8lrtl |title=Gda\u0144ska Ksi\u0105\u017cka Roku 2004 |date=25 February 2005 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Gda\u0144sk Book of the Year 2004}}</ref>\n* 2004 - nagroda ''Media Ksi\u0105\u017cce'' za rok 2004, za zbi\u00f3r ''Stara jak \u015bwiat'' (\"\"Media Book\" award for 2004, for the collection \"Old as the World\"\")<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.kurierzamojski.pl/teresa-ferenc-ze-wsi-sochy/ |title=Teresa Ferenc ze wsi Sochy |last=Ciurysek |first=Agnieszka |date=13 August 2015 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc from the village of Sochy}}</ref>\n* 2013 - fina\u0142 Nagrody Poetyckiej Orfeusz za tom ''Widok na \u017cycie'' (final of the Orpheus Poetry Award for the volume ''A view of life'')<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.orfeusz-nagroda.pl/index.php/finalisci/27-finalisci/finalisci-2013 |title=Finali\u015bci Nagrody Poetyckiej Orfeusz 2013 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Finalists of the Orpheus Poetry Award 2013}}</ref>\n* 2016 - silver [[Medal for Merit to Culture \u2013 Gloria Artis]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://mkidn.gov.pl/pages/posts/wiceminister-sellin-wreczyl-odznaczenia-6633.php |title=Wiceminister Sellin wr\u0119czy\u0142 odznaczenia |date=3 October 2016 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Deputy Minister Sellin presented awards}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://mkidn.gov.pl/pages/strona-glowna/ministerstwo/odznaczenia/medal-zasluzony-kulturze---gloria-artis.php |title=Medal Zas\u0142u\u017cony Kulturze - Gloria Artis. Lista laureat\u00f3w medalu Zas\u0142u\u017cony Kulturze - Gloria Artis. Ferenc Teresa |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Medal for Merit to Culture - Gloria Artis. List of winners of the Medal of Merit to Culture - Gloria Artis. Ferenc Teresa}}</ref>\n\n==Bibliography==\n*{{cite web |url=http://pbl.ibl.poznan.pl/dostep/index.php?s=d_biezacy&f=zapisy&p_tworcaid=174 |title=Polska Bibliografia Literacka. Ferenc Teresa |access-date=14 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Polish Literary Bibliography. Ferenc Teresa}}\n*{{cite web |url=https://www.polskieradio.pl/8/2384/Artykul/1100633,Rzez-w-Sochach-i-rozstrzelali-ich-wszystkich- |title=Rze\u017a w Sochach: ... i rozstrzelali ich wszystkich |date=15 April 2014 |access-date=15 February 2020 |language=pl |trans-title=Slaughter in Sochy: ... and they shot them all}}\n\n==See also==\n{{portal|Poland|Poetry}}\n*[[Anna Janko]]\n*[[Zbigniew Jankowski]]\n*[[Sochy massacre]]\n*[[Ethnic cleansing of Zamojszczyzna by Nazi Germany]]\n*[[Pacification actions in German-occupied Poland]]\n*[[List of Polish-language authors]]\n*[[List of Polish-language poets]]\n*[[List of Poles]]\n*[[Zamo\u015b\u0107]]\n*[[Zwierzyniec]]\n\n== References ==\n<!-- Inline citations added to your article will automatically display here. See en.wikipedia.org/wiki/WP:REFB for instructions on how to add citations. -->\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://yadda.icm.edu.pl/yadda/element/bwmeta1.element.desklight-d0260610-a987-4de7-903e-ceeab2b58d4e Home as Artistic Figure in Teresa Ferenc\u2019s Poetry. A Critical Introduction to the Issue], author Pawlik-Kopek Aleksandra: ''Dom jako figura artystyczna w poezji Teresy Ferenc. Wst\u0119p do problematyki''.\n*[https://poezja.org/wz/Ferenc_Teresa/ PL Teresa Ferenc], poetry\n*{{cite web |url=https://www.kurierzamojski.pl/teresa-ferenc-ze-wsi-sochy/ |title=Teresa Ferenc ze wsi Sochy |last=Ciurysek |first=Agnieszka |date=13 August 2015 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc from the village of Sochy}}\n*{{cite web |url=https://film.wp.pl/wojna-nie-umiera-nigdy-traumatyczne-wspomnienia-przeszly-z-matki-na-corke-6244246498338433a?src01=f1e45 |title=Wojna nie umiera nigdy. Traumatyczne wspomnienia przesz\u0142y z matki na c\u00f3rk\u0119 |last=Zagalski |first=Jakub |date=23 April 2018 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=War never dies. Traumatic memories passed from mother to daughter}}\n*{{cite web |url=https://wiadomosci.onet.pl/gdanska-ksiazka-roku-2004/8lrtl |title=Gda\u0144ska Ksi\u0105\u017cka Roku 2004 |date=25 February 2005 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Gda\u0144sk Book of the Year 2004}}\n*{{cite web |url=https://www.gosc.pl/doc/808289.Milosc-nie-mija |title=Mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 nie mija |last=Gruszka-Zych |first=Barbara |date=27 September 2010 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Love doesn't go by}}\n*{{cite web |url=http://pbl.ibl.poznan.pl/dostep/index.php?s=d_biezacy&f=zapisy&p_tworcaid=174 |title=Polska Bibliografia Literacka. Ferenc Teresa |access-date=14 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Polish Literary Bibliography. Ferenc Teresa}}\n*{{cite web |url=https://www.bookdepository.com/Dzieci-Wody-Teresa-Ferenc/9788391928714 |title=Dzieci Wody: Wiersze Z Morzem. Ferenc Teresa |access-date=14 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Water Children: Poems With The Sea. Ferenc Teresa}}\n*{{cite web |url=https://www.bookdepository.com/Wiersze-Wybor-Teresa-Ferenc/9788364708251 |title=\"Wiersze. Wybor.\" Teresa Ferenc |access-date=14 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=\"Poems. Choice.\" Teresa Ferenc}}\n*{{cite web |url=https://www.amazon.com/Wiersze-Wybor/dp/8364708252 |title=\"Wiersze. Wybor.\" Ferenc Teresa |access-date=14 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=\"Poems. Choice.\" Ferenc Teresa}}\n*{{in lang|pl}} [https://vod.tvp.pl/video/mala-zaglada,mala-zaglada,42034289 Ma\u0142a Zag\u0142ada] film about Sochy massacre \"A Minor Genocide\" (Ma\u0142a Zag\u0142ada)\n*{{IMDb title|8655702|Ma\u0142a zag\u0142ada}} \"A Minor Genocide\" film about [[Sochy massacre]]\n* ''[https://sales.tvp.pl/38627855/a-minor-genocide A Minor Genocide]'', Film ''A Minor Genocide'' in [[Telewizja Polska|TVP]]\n* {{cite web |url=https://vod.tvp.pl/video/mala-zaglada,mala-zaglada,42034289 |title=Ma\u0142a zag\u0142ada |access-date=15 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=\"A Minor Genocide\"}}, Teresa Ferenc in a documentary film ''Ma\u0142a zag\u0142ada''\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Ferenc, Teresa}}\n[[Category:1934 births]]\n[[Category:Polish schoolteachers]]\n[[Category:Polish women poets]]\n[[Category:People from Rybnik]]\n[[Category:People from Zamo\u015b\u0107 County]]\n[[Category:Recipients of the Silver Medal for Merit to Culture \u2013 Gloria Artis]]\n[[Category:20th-century Polish poets]]\n[[Category:21st-century Polish poets]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox writer\n| name        = Teresa Ferenc\n| image       =\n| caption     =\n| birth_name  =\n| birth_date  = {{birth date|1934|4|27|}}\n| birth_place = [[Rusz\u00f3w-Kolonia]], [[Lublin Voivodeship]], [[Poland]]\n| death_date  =\n| death_place =\n| occupation  = [[poet]]\n| nationality = Polish\n| spouse      = [[Zbigniew Jankowski]]\n| awards      = [[Medal for Merit to Culture \u2013 Gloria Artis]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://mkidn.gov.pl/pages/posts/wiceminister-sellin-wreczyl-odznaczenia-6633.php |title=Wiceminister Sellin wr\u0119czy\u0142 odznaczenia |date=3 October 2016 |access-date=13 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Deputy Minister Sellin presented awards}}</ref>\n| signature   =\n}}\n'''Teresa Ferenc''' (27 April 1934)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://latarnia-morska.eu/pl/port-literacki/906-qwidok-na-ycieq-teresy-ferenc |title=Teresa Ferenc \"Widok na \u017cycie\", Towarzystwo Przyjaci\u00f3\u0142 Sopotu, Sopot 2012, str. 64 |access-date=14 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc \"Widok na \u017bycie\", Society of Friends of Sopot, Sopot 2012, p. 64}}</ref>, is a [[Poles|Polish]] [[poet]].<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.polskieradio.pl/8/2384/Artykul/1100633,Rzez-w-Sochach-i-rozstrzelali-ich-wszystkich- |title=Rze\u017a w Sochach: ... i rozstrzelali ich wszystkich |date=15 April 2014 |access-date=15 February 2020 |language=pl |trans-title=Slaughter in Sochy: ... and they shot them all}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.gosc.pl/doc/808289.Milosc-nie-mija |title=Mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 nie mija |last=Gruszka-Zych |first=Barbara |date=27 September 2010 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Love doesn't go by}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.worldcat.org/search?q=au%3AFerenc%2C+Teresa.&qt=hot_author |title=World Cat. Ferenc Teresa |access-date=14 February 2020 |language=English |trans-title=World Cat. Ferenc Teresa}}</ref>\n\n==Life==\n[[File:Bukowa gora rafal pikul.jpg|thumb|[[Sochy, Lublin Voivodeship]], the village where Teresa Ferenc lived up to 9 years old. View from Bukowa G\u00f3ra]]\nTeresa Ferenc was born in [[Rusz\u00f3w-Kolonia]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://latarnia-morska.eu/pl/port-literacki/906-qwidok-na-ycieq-teresy-ferenc |title=Teresa Ferenc \"Widok na \u017cycie\", Towarzystwo Przyjaci\u00f3\u0142 Sopotu, Sopot 2012, str. 64 |access-date=14 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc \"Widok na \u017bycie\", Society of Friends of Sopot, Sopot 2012, p. 64}}</ref> in the administrative district of [[Gmina \u0141abunie]], within [[Zamo\u015b\u0107 County]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://latarnia-morska.eu/pl/port-literacki/906-qwidok-na-ycieq-teresy-ferenc |title=Teresa Ferenc \"Widok na \u017cycie\", Towarzystwo Przyjaci\u00f3\u0142 Sopotu, Sopot 2012, str. 64 |access-date=14 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc \"Widok na \u017bycie\", Society of Friends of Sopot, Sopot 2012, p. 64}}</ref> in [[Lublin Voivodeship]] in [[Poland]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.kurierzamojski.pl/teresa-ferenc-ze-wsi-sochy/ |title=Teresa Ferenc ze wsi Sochy |last=Ciurysek |first=Agnieszka |date=13 August 2015 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc from the village of Sochy}}</ref>. She lived with her parents and family in the village of [[Sochy, Lublin Voivodeship]] in the [[Zamo\u015b\u0107]] region<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.gosc.pl/doc/808289.Milosc-nie-mija |title=Mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 nie mija |last=Gruszka-Zych |first=Barbara |date=27 September 2010 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Love doesn't go by}}</ref>. During [[World War II]], as a 9-year-old child, she survived the [[Sochy massacre|massacre of the village of Sochy]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.polskieradio.pl/8/2384/Artykul/1100633,Rzez-w-Sochach-i-rozstrzelali-ich-wszystkich- |title=Rze\u017a w Sochach: ... i rozstrzelali ich wszystkich |date=15 April 2014 |access-date=15 February 2020 |language=pl |trans-title=Slaughter in Sochy: ... and they shot them all}}</ref> by [[Nazi Germany]] on June 1, 1943 during [[Occupation of Poland (1939\u20131945)|German occupation of Poland (1939\u20131945)]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.polskieradio.pl/8/2384/Artykul/1100633,Rzez-w-Sochach-i-rozstrzelali-ich-wszystkich- |title=Rze\u017a w Sochach: ... i rozstrzelali ich wszystkich |date=15 April 2014 |access-date=15 February 2020 |language=pl |trans-title=Slaughter in Sochy: ... and they shot them all}}</ref>. Her parents were murdered then<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.polskieradio.pl/8/2384/Artykul/1100633,Rzez-w-Sochach-i-rozstrzelali-ich-wszystkich- |title=Rze\u017a w Sochach: ... i rozstrzelali ich wszystkich |date=15 April 2014 |access-date=15 February 2020 |language=pl |trans-title=Slaughter in Sochy: ... and they shot them all}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.kurierzamojski.pl/teresa-ferenc-ze-wsi-sochy/ |title=Teresa Ferenc ze wsi Sochy |last=Ciurysek |first=Agnieszka |date=13 August 2015 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc from the village of Sochy}}</ref>. The village was also bombed by German [[Luftwaffe]] planes<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.polskieradio.pl/8/2384/Artykul/1100633,Rzez-w-Sochach-i-rozstrzelali-ich-wszystkich- |title=Rze\u017a w Sochach: ... i rozstrzelali ich wszystkich |date=15 April 2014 |access-date=15 February 2020 |language=pl |trans-title=Slaughter in Sochy: ... and they shot them all}}</ref><ref>{{cite book |last=Lukas |first=Richard C. |author-link=Richard C. Lukas |date=2012 |title=Zapomniany Holokaust. Polacy pod okupacj\u0105 niemieck\u0105 1939-1945 |trans-title=The Forgotten Holocaust. The Poles Under German Occupation, 1939-1944 |url= |language=pl |location=Pozna\u0144 |publisher=Dom Wydawniczy Rebis |isbn=978-83-7510-832-3}}, p. 68.</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://film.wp.pl/wojna-nie-umiera-nigdy-traumatyczne-wspomnienia-przeszly-z-matki-na-corke-6244246498338433a?src01=f1e45 |title=Wojna nie umiera nigdy. Traumatyczne wspomnienia przesz\u0142y z matki na c\u00f3rk\u0119 |last=Zagalski |first=Jakub |date=23 April 2018 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=War never dies. Traumatic memories passed from mother to daughter}}</ref>. As an orphan, she was raised in relatives and in orphanages<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.kurierzamojski.pl/teresa-ferenc-ze-wsi-sochy/ |title=Teresa Ferenc ze wsi Sochy |last=Ciurysek |first=Agnieszka |date=13 August 2015 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc from the village of Sochy}}</ref>. After graduating from ''Teacher's College'', she taught at the Lyceum in [[Rybnik]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.kurierzamojski.pl/teresa-ferenc-ze-wsi-sochy/ |title=Teresa Ferenc ze wsi Sochy |last=Ciurysek |first=Agnieszka |date=13 August 2015 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc from the village of Sochy}}</ref>. In 1956 she married the poet [[Zbigniew Jankowski]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.kurierzamojski.pl/teresa-ferenc-ze-wsi-sochy/ |title=Teresa Ferenc ze wsi Sochy |last=Ciurysek |first=Agnieszka |date=13 August 2015 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc from the village of Sochy}}</ref>. She raised two daughters, also a poet: [[Anna Janko]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.amazon.com/Little-Annihilation-Anna-Janko/dp/1642860662 |title=A Little Annihilation |access-date=15 February 2020 |language=English}}</ref> and Milena Wieczorek<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.gosc.pl/doc/808289.Milosc-nie-mija |title=Mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 nie mija |last=Gruszka-Zych |first=Barbara |date=27 September 2010 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Love doesn't go by}}</ref>.\n\nAs a poet she debuted in 1958<ref>{{cite web |url=http://mkidn.gov.pl/pages/posts/wiceminister-sellin-wreczyl-odznaczenia-6633.php |title=Wiceminister Sellin wr\u0119czy\u0142 odznaczenia |date=3 October 2016 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Deputy Minister Sellin presented awards}}</ref>. Her first published book of poems was ''Moje ry\u017cowe poletko'' (\"My rice field\") in 1964<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.worldcat.org/search?q=au%3AFerenc%2C+Teresa.&qt=hot_author |title=World Cat. Ferenc Teresa |access-date=14 February 2020 |language=English |trans-title=World Cat. Ferenc Teresa}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://mkidn.gov.pl/pages/posts/wiceminister-sellin-wreczyl-odznaczenia-6633.php |title=Wiceminister Sellin wr\u0119czy\u0142 odznaczenia |date=3 October 2016 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Deputy Minister Sellin presented awards}}</ref>. Teresa Ferenc's works have appeared in dozens of anthologies and other collective publications in Poland and abroad<ref>{{cite web |url=http://mkidn.gov.pl/pages/posts/wiceminister-sellin-wreczyl-odznaczenia-6633.php |title=Wiceminister Sellin wr\u0119czy\u0142 odznaczenia |date=3 October 2016 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Deputy Minister Sellin presented awards}}</ref>. She also published books with poems for children<ref>{{cite web |url=http://mkidn.gov.pl/pages/posts/wiceminister-sellin-wreczyl-odznaczenia-6633.php |title=Wiceminister Sellin wr\u0119czy\u0142 odznaczenia |date=3 October 2016 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Deputy Minister Sellin presented awards}}</ref>. Together with her husband Zbigniew Jankowski, she founded the poetic group \"Reda\"<ref>{{cite book |last=Kuncewicz |first=Piotr |date=1995 |title=Leksykon polskich pisarzy wsp\u00f3\u0142czesnych |trans-title=Lexicon of Polish contemporary writers |language=pl |location=Warsaw |publisher=Graf-Punkt |isbn=83-86091-29-0}}, p. 219.</ref>. In 2004 and 2009 she was the laureate of the President of the City of [[Gda\u0144sk]] Award in the Field of Culture.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.gdansk.pl/urzad-miejski/biuro-prezydenta-ds-kultury/laureaci-nagrody-prezydenta-miasta-gdanska-w-dziedzinie-kultury,a,27578 |title=Laureaci Nagrody Prezydenta Miasta Gda\u0144ska w Dziedzinie Kultury |access-date=30 January 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Winners of the Award of the Mayor of the City of Gda\u0144sk in the Field of Culture}}</ref>\n\nShe is a member of the [[PEN Club]] and a founding member of the [[Stowarzyszenie Pisarzy Polskich|Polish Writers' Association]] (SPP)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://mkidn.gov.pl/pages/posts/wiceminister-sellin-wreczyl-odznaczenia-6633.php |title=Wiceminister Sellin wr\u0119czy\u0142 odznaczenia |date=3 October 2016 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Deputy Minister Sellin presented awards}}</ref>. The poet publishes, among others in ''[[Tw\u00f3rczo\u015b\u0107]]'' (\"Creativity\"), ''[[Odra (magazine)]]'', ''Topos''<ref>{{cite web |url=http://owvolumen.pl/sklep-2/biblioteka-poezji-polskiej/teresa-ferenc-wiersze-wybor/ |title=Teresa Ferenc. ''Wiersze. Wyb\u00f3r'' |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc. \"Poems. Choice}}</ref>.\n\nIn 2016, Teresa Ferenc with her husband [[Zbigniew Jankowski]] was awarded the silver \"[[Medal for Merit to Culture \u2013 Gloria Artis]]\".<ref>{{cite web |url=http://mkidn.gov.pl/pages/posts/wiceminister-sellin-wreczyl-odznaczenia-6633.php |title=Wiceminister Sellin wr\u0119czy\u0142 odznaczenia |date=3 October 2016 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Deputy Minister Sellin presented awards}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://mkidn.gov.pl/pages/strona-glowna/ministerstwo/odznaczenia/medal-zasluzony-kulturze---gloria-artis.php |title=Medal Zas\u0142u\u017cony Kulturze - Gloria Artis. Lista laureat\u00f3w medalu Zas\u0142u\u017cony Kulturze - Gloria Artis. Ferenc Teresa |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Medal for Merit to Culture - Gloria Artis. List of winners of the Medal of Merit to Culture - Gloria Artis. Ferenc Teresa}}</ref>\n\n==Teresa Ferenc in film and books==\nDramatic events in the life of Teresa Ferenc, when she survived as a 9-year-old child, the [[Sochy massacre]] by the German occupiers on June 1, 1943, in which she lost both [[parents]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.polskieradio.pl/8/2384/Artykul/1100633,Rzez-w-Sochach-i-rozstrzelali-ich-wszystkich- |title=Rze\u017a w Sochach: ... i rozstrzelali ich wszystkich |date=15 April 2014 |access-date=15 February 2020 |language=pl |trans-title=Slaughter in Sochy: ... and they shot them all}}</ref> - she described in her book titled ''Ma\u0142a Zag\u0142ada'' (\"A Little Annihilation\"), her daughter poet [[Anna Janko]].<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.amazon.com/Little-Annihilation-Anna-Janko/dp/1642860662 |title=A Little Annihilation |access-date=15 February 2020 |language=English}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/50356627-a-little-annihilation |title=A Little Annihilation by Anna Janko, Philip Boehm (Translator) |access-date=15 February 2020 |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.polskieradio.pl/8/2384/Artykul/1100633,Rzez-w-Sochach-i-rozstrzelali-ich-wszystkich- |title=Rze\u017a w Sochach: ... i rozstrzelali ich wszystkich |date=15 April 2014 |access-date=15 February 2020 |language=pl |trans-title=Slaughter in Sochy: ... and they shot them all}}</ref>\n\nThe book ''Ma\u0142a Zag\u0142ada'' (\"A Little Annihilation\") by Anna Janko became the canvas for the creation of the film [[Natalia Koryncka-Gruz]] entitled \"A Minor Genocide\" (''Ma\u0142a zag\u0142ada'')<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.imdb.com/title/tt8655702/ |title=Ma\u0142a zag\u0142ada (2018) |access-date=15 February 2020 |language=English |trans-title=Mala zaglada (original title) \"A Minor Genocide\"}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://vod.tvp.pl/video/mala-zaglada,mala-zaglada,42034289 |title=Ma\u0142a zag\u0142ada |access-date=15 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=\"A Minor Genocide\"}}</ref>. The film reminds the tragic fate of Teresa Ferenc and the inhabitants of the village of [[Sochy, Lublin Voivodeship|Sochy]] in the Zamo\u015b\u0107 region, victims of the [[massacre]]. The consequences of war and war crimes in subsequent generations, families of victims of [[genocide]] are also shown.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.amazon.com/Little-Annihilation-Anna-Janko/dp/1642860662 |title=A Little Annihilation |access-date=15 February 2020 |language=English}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/50356627-a-little-annihilation |title=A Little Annihilation by Anna Janko, Philip Boehm (Translator) |access-date=15 February 2020 |language=en}}</ref><ref>''[https://sales.tvp.pl/38627855/a-minor-genocide A Minor Genocide]'', Film ''A Minor Genocide'' in [[Telewizja Polska|TVP]]</ref>\n\n==Selected works==\n* ''Moje ry\u017cowe poletko'' (\"My rice field\") (1964)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://latarnia-morska.eu/pl/port-literacki/906-qwidok-na-ycieq-teresy-ferenc |title=Teresa Ferenc \"Widok na \u017cycie\", Towarzystwo Przyjaci\u00f3\u0142 Sopotu, Sopot 2012, str. 64 |access-date=14 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc \"Widok na \u017bycie\", Society of Friends of Sopot, Sopot 2012, p. 64}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://mkidn.gov.pl/pages/posts/wiceminister-sellin-wreczyl-odznaczenia-6633.php |title=Wiceminister Sellin wr\u0119czy\u0142 odznaczenia |date=3 October 2016 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Deputy Minister Sellin presented awards}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.worldcat.org/search?q=au%3AFerenc%2C+Teresa.&qt=hot_author |title=World Cat. Ferenc Teresa |access-date=14 February 2020 |language=English |trans-title=World Cat. Ferenc Teresa}}</ref>,\n* ''Zal\u0105\u017cnia'' (\"Ovary\") (1968)<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.kurierzamojski.pl/teresa-ferenc-ze-wsi-sochy/ |title=Teresa Ferenc ze wsi Sochy |last=Ciurysek |first=Agnieszka |date=13 August 2015 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc from the village of Sochy}}</ref>,\n* ''Godno\u015b\u0107 natury'' (\"Dignity of nature\") (1973)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://latarnia-morska.eu/pl/port-literacki/906-qwidok-na-ycieq-teresy-ferenc |title=Teresa Ferenc \"Widok na \u017cycie\", Towarzystwo Przyjaci\u00f3\u0142 Sopotu, Sopot 2012, str. 64 |access-date=14 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc \"Widok na \u017bycie\", Society of Friends of Sopot, Sopot 2012, p. 64}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.kurierzamojski.pl/teresa-ferenc-ze-wsi-sochy/ |title=Teresa Ferenc ze wsi Sochy |last=Ciurysek |first=Agnieszka |date=13 August 2015 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc from the village of Sochy}}</ref>,\n* ''Cia\u0142o i p\u0142omie\u0144'' (\"Body and flame\") (1974)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://mkidn.gov.pl/pages/posts/wiceminister-sellin-wreczyl-odznaczenia-6633.php |title=Wiceminister Sellin wr\u0119czy\u0142 odznaczenia |date=3 October 2016 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Deputy Minister Sellin presented awards}}</ref>,\n* ''Ma\u0142\u017ce\u0144stwo'' (\"Marriage\") (1975)<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.kurierzamojski.pl/teresa-ferenc-ze-wsi-sochy/ |title=Teresa Ferenc ze wsi Sochy |last=Ciurysek |first=Agnieszka |date=13 August 2015 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc from the village of Sochy}}</ref>,\n* ''Poezje wybrane i nowe'' (\"Selected and new poetry\") (1975)<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.kurierzamojski.pl/teresa-ferenc-ze-wsi-sochy/ |title=Teresa Ferenc ze wsi Sochy |last=Ciurysek |first=Agnieszka |date=13 August 2015 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc from the village of Sochy}}</ref>,\n* ''Wypalona dolina'' (\"Burned Valley\") (1979)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://latarnia-morska.eu/pl/port-literacki/906-qwidok-na-ycieq-teresy-ferenc |title=Teresa Ferenc \"Widok na \u017cycie\", Towarzystwo Przyjaci\u00f3\u0142 Sopotu, Sopot 2012, str. 64 |access-date=14 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc \"Widok na \u017bycie\", Society of Friends of Sopot, Sopot 2012, p. 64}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://mkidn.gov.pl/pages/posts/wiceminister-sellin-wreczyl-odznaczenia-6633.php |title=Wiceminister Sellin wr\u0119czy\u0142 odznaczenia |date=3 October 2016 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Deputy Minister Sellin presented awards}}</ref>,\n* ''Poezje wybrane'' (\"Selected poetry\") (1980)<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.kurierzamojski.pl/teresa-ferenc-ze-wsi-sochy/ |title=Teresa Ferenc ze wsi Sochy |last=Ciurysek |first=Agnieszka |date=13 August 2015 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc from the village of Sochy}}</ref>,\n* ''Pieta'' (\"[[Piet\u00e0]]\") (1981)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://mkidn.gov.pl/pages/posts/wiceminister-sellin-wreczyl-odznaczenia-6633.php |title=Wiceminister Sellin wr\u0119czy\u0142 odznaczenia |date=3 October 2016 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Deputy Minister Sellin presented awards}}</ref>,\n* ''Najbli\u017csza ojczyzna'' (\"Nearest homeland\") (1982)<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.kurierzamojski.pl/teresa-ferenc-ze-wsi-sochy/ |title=Teresa Ferenc ze wsi Sochy |last=Ciurysek |first=Agnieszka |date=13 August 2015 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc from the village of Sochy}}</ref>,\n* ''Grzeszny pacierz'' (\"A sinful prayer\") (1983)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://mkidn.gov.pl/pages/posts/wiceminister-sellin-wreczyl-odznaczenia-6633.php |title=Wiceminister Sellin wr\u0119czy\u0142 odznaczenia |date=3 October 2016 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Deputy Minister Sellin presented awards}}</ref>.\n* ''Drzewo dziwo'' (\"Amazingly tree\") (1987)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://pbl.ibl.poznan.pl/dostep/index.php?s=d_biezacy&f=zapisy&p_tworcaid=174 |title=Polska Bibliografia Literacka. Ferenc Teresa |access-date=14 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Polish Literary Bibliography. Ferenc Teresa}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.kurierzamojski.pl/teresa-ferenc-ze-wsi-sochy/ |title=Teresa Ferenc ze wsi Sochy |last=Ciurysek |first=Agnieszka |date=13 August 2015 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc from the village of Sochy}}</ref>,\n* ''N\u00f3\u017c za ptakiem'' (\"Knife behind the bird\") (1987)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://pbl.ibl.poznan.pl/dostep/index.php?s=d_biezacy&f=zapisy&p_tworcaid=174 |title=Polska Bibliografia Literacka. Ferenc Teresa |access-date=14 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Polish Literary Bibliography. Ferenc Teresa}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://mkidn.gov.pl/pages/posts/wiceminister-sellin-wreczyl-odznaczenia-6633.php |title=Wiceminister Sellin wr\u0119czy\u0142 odznaczenia |date=3 October 2016 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Deputy Minister Sellin presented awards}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://latarnia-morska.eu/pl/port-literacki/906-qwidok-na-ycieq-teresy-ferenc |title=Teresa Ferenc \"Widok na \u017cycie\", Towarzystwo Przyjaci\u00f3\u0142 Sopotu, Sopot 2012, str. 64 |access-date=14 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc \"Widok na \u017bycie\", Society of Friends of Sopot, Sopot 2012, p. 64}}</ref>,\n* ''Kradzione w raju'' (1988)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://pbl.ibl.poznan.pl/dostep/index.php?s=d_biezacy&f=zapisy&p_tworcaid=174 |title=Polska Bibliografia Literacka. Ferenc Teresa |access-date=14 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Polish Literary Bibliography. Ferenc Teresa}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.kurierzamojski.pl/teresa-ferenc-ze-wsi-sochy/ |title=Teresa Ferenc ze wsi Sochy |last=Ciurysek |first=Agnieszka |date=13 August 2015 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc from the village of Sochy}}</ref>,\n* ''Wyb\u00f3r wierszy'' ''Swallowing Paradise. Poems.'' (1992) (in [[United States]])<ref>{{cite web |url=http://pbl.ibl.poznan.pl/dostep/index.php?s=d_biezacy&f=zapisy&p_tworcaid=174 |title=Polska Bibliografia Literacka. Ferenc Teresa |access-date=14 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Polish Literary Bibliography. Ferenc Teresa}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://latarnia-morska.eu/pl/port-literacki/906-qwidok-na-ycieq-teresy-ferenc |title=Teresa Ferenc \"Widok na \u017cycie\", Towarzystwo Przyjaci\u00f3\u0142 Sopotu, Sopot 2012, str. 64 |access-date=14 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc \"Widok na \u017bycie\", Society of Friends of Sopot, Sopot 2012, p. 64}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://pbl.ibl.poznan.pl/dostep/index.php?s=d_biezacy&f=zapisy_szczeg&p_zapis=196281 |title=Polska Bibliografia Literacka. Ferenc Teresa. ''Swallowing Paradise. Poems'' (1992) (Chattanooga: The Poetry Miscellany Chapbooks) |access-date=14 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Polish Literary Bibliography. Ferenc Teresa. ''Swallowing Paradise. Poems'' (1992) (Chattanooga: The Poetry Miscellany Chapbooks)}}</ref>,\n* ''Wiersze'' (\"Poems\") (1994)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://pbl.ibl.poznan.pl/dostep/index.php?s=d_biezacy&f=zapisy&p_tworcaid=174 |title=Polska Bibliografia Literacka. Ferenc Teresa |access-date=14 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Polish Literary Bibliography. Ferenc Teresa}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.kurierzamojski.pl/teresa-ferenc-ze-wsi-sochy/ |title=Teresa Ferenc ze wsi Sochy |last=Ciurysek |first=Agnieszka |date=13 August 2015 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc from the village of Sochy}}</ref>,\n* ''Bo\u017ce pole'' (\"God's field\") (1997)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://pbl.ibl.poznan.pl/dostep/index.php?s=d_biezacy&f=zapisy&p_tworcaid=174 |title=Polska Bibliografia Literacka. Ferenc Teresa |access-date=14 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Polish Literary Bibliography. Ferenc Teresa}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://mkidn.gov.pl/pages/posts/wiceminister-sellin-wreczyl-odznaczenia-6633.php |title=Wiceminister Sellin wr\u0119czy\u0142 odznaczenia |date=3 October 2016 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Deputy Minister Sellin presented awards}}</ref>,\n* ''Psalmy i inne wiersze dawne i nowe'' (\"Psalms and other old and new poems\") (1999)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://pbl.ibl.poznan.pl/dostep/index.php?s=d_biezacy&f=zapisy&p_tworcaid=174 |title=Polska Bibliografia Literacka. Ferenc Teresa |access-date=14 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Polish Literary Bibliography. Ferenc Teresa}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.kurierzamojski.pl/teresa-ferenc-ze-wsi-sochy/ |title=Teresa Ferenc ze wsi Sochy |last=Ciurysek |first=Agnieszka |date=13 August 2015 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc from the village of Sochy}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://latarnia-morska.eu/pl/port-literacki/906-qwidok-na-ycieq-teresy-ferenc |title=Teresa Ferenc \"Widok na \u017cycie\", Towarzystwo Przyjaci\u00f3\u0142 Sopotu, Sopot 2012, str. 64 |access-date=14 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc \"Widok na \u017bycie\", Society of Friends of Sopot, Sopot 2012, p. 64}}</ref>,\n* ''Dzieci wody'' (\"Water children\") (2003)<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bookdepository.com/Dzieci-Wody-Teresa-Ferenc/9788391928714 |title=Dzieci Wody: Wiersze Z Morzem. Ferenc Teresa |access-date=14 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Water Children: Poems With The Sea. Ferenc Teresa}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://pbl.ibl.poznan.pl/dostep/index.php?s=d_biezacy&f=zapisy&p_tworcaid=174 |title=Polska Bibliografia Literacka. Ferenc Teresa |access-date=14 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Polish Literary Bibliography. Ferenc Teresa}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.kurierzamojski.pl/teresa-ferenc-ze-wsi-sochy/ |title=Teresa Ferenc ze wsi Sochy |last=Ciurysek |first=Agnieszka |date=13 August 2015 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc from the village of Sochy}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://latarnia-morska.eu/pl/port-literacki/906-qwidok-na-ycieq-teresy-ferenc |title=Teresa Ferenc \"Widok na \u017cycie\", Towarzystwo Przyjaci\u00f3\u0142 Sopotu, Sopot 2012, str. 64 |access-date=14 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc \"Widok na \u017bycie\", Society of Friends of Sopot, Sopot 2012, p. 64}}</ref>,\n* ''Stara jak \u015bwiat'' (\"Old as the world\") (2004)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://mkidn.gov.pl/pages/posts/wiceminister-sellin-wreczyl-odznaczenia-6633.php |title=Wiceminister Sellin wr\u0119czy\u0142 odznaczenia |date=3 October 2016 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Deputy Minister Sellin presented awards}}</ref>,\n* ''Ogniopis. Wyb\u00f3r wierszy'' (\"Ogniopis. Selection of poems\") (2009)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://latarnia-morska.eu/pl/port-literacki/906-qwidok-na-ycieq-teresy-ferenc |title=Teresa Ferenc \"Widok na \u017cycie\", Towarzystwo Przyjaci\u00f3\u0142 Sopotu, Sopot 2012, str. 64 |access-date=14 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc \"Widok na \u017bycie\", Society of Friends of Sopot, Sopot 2012, p. 64}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://mkidn.gov.pl/pages/posts/wiceminister-sellin-wreczyl-odznaczenia-6633.php |title=Wiceminister Sellin wr\u0119czy\u0142 odznaczenia |date=3 October 2016 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Deputy Minister Sellin presented awards}}</ref>,\n* ''Widok na \u017cycie'' (\"A view of life\") (2012)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://latarnia-morska.eu/pl/port-literacki/906-qwidok-na-ycieq-teresy-ferenc |title=Teresa Ferenc \"Widok na \u017cycie\", Towarzystwo Przyjaci\u00f3\u0142 Sopotu, Sopot 2012, str. 64 |access-date=14 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc \"Widok na \u017bycie\", Society of Friends of Sopot, Sopot 2012, p. 64}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://mkidn.gov.pl/pages/posts/wiceminister-sellin-wreczyl-odznaczenia-6633.php |title=Wiceminister Sellin wr\u0119czy\u0142 odznaczenia |date=3 October 2016 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Deputy Minister Sellin presented awards}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.worldcat.org/search?q=au%3AFerenc%2C+Teresa.&qt=hot_author |title=World Cat. Ferenc Teresa |access-date=14 February 2020 |language=English |trans-title=World Cat. Ferenc Teresa}}</ref>\n* ''Wiersze. Wybor'' (\"Poems. Choice\") (2017)<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.amazon.com/Wiersze-Wybor/dp/8364708252 |title=\"Wiersze. Wybor.\" Ferenc Teresa |access-date=14 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=\"Poems. Choice.\" Ferenc Teresa}}</ref>\n\n==Characteristics of creativity==\nIn his poetry, he touches on topics related to love, corporeality and motherhood. In her poetry she also often returns to the tragedy of her childhood - in 1943, as a nine-year-old child, she witnessed how almost all residents (including her [[parents]]) were shot by the [[Germans]]; the village itself was then bombed and burned (hence the fire motif returns in its poetry)<ref>{{cite book |last=Kuncewicz |first=Piotr |date=1995 |title=Leksykon polskich pisarzy wsp\u00f3\u0142czesnych |trans-title=Lexicon of Polish contemporary writers |language=pl |location=Warsaw |publisher=Graf-Punkt |isbn=83-86091-29-0}}, p. 219.</ref><ref>{{cite book |last=Borkowska |first=Gra\u017cyna |last2=Czermi\u0144ska |first2=Ma\u0142gorzata |last3=Philips |first3=Ursula |date=2000 |title=Pisarki polskie od \u015bredniowiecza do wsp\u00f3\u0142czesno\u015bci |trans-title=Polish writers from the Middle Ages to the present day |language=Polish |location=Gda\u0144sk |publisher=S\u0142owo Obraz Terytoria |isbn=83-87316-74-1}}</ref>.\n\nTeresa Ferenc wrote in poem ''Wie\u015b skamienia\u0142a'' (poem: \"The village is petrified\") about the [[Sochy massacre]], which she survived in her childhood:<br />\"June 1, 1943 on the edge of the [[Zwierzyniec]] forests\nmy village was shot.<br />[[Sochy, Lublin Voivodeship|Sochy]] - like in [[Oradour-sur-Glane massacre|Oradour]] in [[France]],<br />Sochy - like in [[Lidice massacre|Lidice]] in [[Czech Republic]],<br />Sochy - like in [[Sant'Anna di Stazzema massacre|Mezzinote]] in [[Italy]].\"<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.kurierzamojski.pl/teresa-ferenc-ze-wsi-sochy/ |title=Teresa Ferenc ze wsi Sochy |last=Ciurysek |first=Agnieszka |date=13 August 2015 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc from the village of Sochy}}, ''Wie\u015b skamienia\u0142a'' (poem: \"The village is petrified\")</ref>\n\n==Selected awards and nominations==\n* 1979 - Nagroda im. Stanis\u0142awa Pi\u0119taka (''Gda\u0144ska Ksi\u0105\u017cka Roku 1979'' w dziedzinie poezji) za tom poezji ''Wypalona dolina'' (\"The prize Stanis\u0142aw Pi\u0119tak ('' Gda\u0144sk Book of the Year 1979 '' in the field of poetry) for the poetry volume \"Burned Valley\"\")<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.kurierzamojski.pl/teresa-ferenc-ze-wsi-sochy/ |title=Teresa Ferenc ze wsi Sochy |last=Ciurysek |first=Agnieszka |date=13 August 2015 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc from the village of Sochy}}</ref>\n* 1997 - wyr\u00f3\u017cnienie przyznane przez Fundacj\u0119 Kultury za ''Bo\u017ce pole'' (\"distinction awarded by the Culture Foundation for \"God's field\"\")<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.kurierzamojski.pl/teresa-ferenc-ze-wsi-sochy/ |title=Teresa Ferenc ze wsi Sochy |last=Ciurysek |first=Agnieszka |date=13 August 2015 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc from the village of Sochy}}</ref>\n* 1997 - nagroda ''Media Ksi\u0105\u017cce'' (''Gda\u0144ska Ksi\u0105\u017cka Wiosny'') za ''Bo\u017ce pole'' (\"''Media Book'' award (''Gda\u0144sk Spring Book'') for \"God's field\"\")<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.kurierzamojski.pl/teresa-ferenc-ze-wsi-sochy/ |title=Teresa Ferenc ze wsi Sochy |last=Ciurysek |first=Agnieszka |date=13 August 2015 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc from the village of Sochy}}</ref>\n* 2004 - ''Nagroda Artusa 2004'' za zbi\u00f3r ''Stara jak \u015bwiat'' (\"\"Artus Award 2004\" for the collection \"Old as the World\"\")<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.kurierzamojski.pl/teresa-ferenc-ze-wsi-sochy/ |title=Teresa Ferenc ze wsi Sochy |last=Ciurysek |first=Agnieszka |date=13 August 2015 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc from the village of Sochy}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://wiadomosci.onet.pl/gdanska-ksiazka-roku-2004/8lrtl |title=Gda\u0144ska Ksi\u0105\u017cka Roku 2004 |date=25 February 2005 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Gda\u0144sk Book of the Year 2004}}</ref>\n* 2004 - nagroda ''Media Ksi\u0105\u017cce'' za rok 2004, za zbi\u00f3r ''Stara jak \u015bwiat'' (\"\"Media Book\" award for 2004, for the collection \"Old as the World\"\")<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.kurierzamojski.pl/teresa-ferenc-ze-wsi-sochy/ |title=Teresa Ferenc ze wsi Sochy |last=Ciurysek |first=Agnieszka |date=13 August 2015 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc from the village of Sochy}}</ref>\n* 2013 - fina\u0142 Nagrody Poetyckiej Orfeusz za tom ''Widok na \u017cycie'' (final of the Orpheus Poetry Award for the volume ''A view of life'')<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.orfeusz-nagroda.pl/index.php/finalisci/27-finalisci/finalisci-2013 |title=Finali\u015bci Nagrody Poetyckiej Orfeusz 2013 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Finalists of the Orpheus Poetry Award 2013}}</ref>\n* 2016 - silver [[Medal for Merit to Culture \u2013 Gloria Artis]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://mkidn.gov.pl/pages/posts/wiceminister-sellin-wreczyl-odznaczenia-6633.php |title=Wiceminister Sellin wr\u0119czy\u0142 odznaczenia |date=3 October 2016 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Deputy Minister Sellin presented awards}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://mkidn.gov.pl/pages/strona-glowna/ministerstwo/odznaczenia/medal-zasluzony-kulturze---gloria-artis.php |title=Medal Zas\u0142u\u017cony Kulturze - Gloria Artis. Lista laureat\u00f3w medalu Zas\u0142u\u017cony Kulturze - Gloria Artis. Ferenc Teresa |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Medal for Merit to Culture - Gloria Artis. List of winners of the Medal of Merit to Culture - Gloria Artis. Ferenc Teresa}}</ref>\n\n==Bibliography==\n*{{cite web |url=http://pbl.ibl.poznan.pl/dostep/index.php?s=d_biezacy&f=zapisy&p_tworcaid=174 |title=Polska Bibliografia Literacka. Ferenc Teresa |access-date=14 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Polish Literary Bibliography. Ferenc Teresa}}\n*{{cite web |url=https://www.polskieradio.pl/8/2384/Artykul/1100633,Rzez-w-Sochach-i-rozstrzelali-ich-wszystkich- |title=Rze\u017a w Sochach: ... i rozstrzelali ich wszystkich |date=15 April 2014 |access-date=15 February 2020 |language=pl |trans-title=Slaughter in Sochy: ... and they shot them all}}\n\n==See also==\n{{portal|Poland|Poetry}}\n*[[Anna Janko]]\n*[[Zbigniew Jankowski]]\n*[[Sochy massacre]]\n*[[Ethnic cleansing of Zamojszczyzna by Nazi Germany]]\n*[[Pacification actions in German-occupied Poland]]\n*[[List of Polish-language authors]]\n*[[List of Polish-language poets]]\n*[[List of Poles]]\n*[[Zamo\u015b\u0107]]\n*[[Zwierzyniec]]\n\n\n== References ==\n<!-- Inline citations added to your article will automatically display here. See en.wikipedia.org/wiki/WP:REFB for instructions on how to add citations. -->\n{{reflist}}\n\n\n\n==External links==\n*[http://yadda.icm.edu.pl/yadda/element/bwmeta1.element.desklight-d0260610-a987-4de7-903e-ceeab2b58d4e Home as Artistic Figure in Teresa Ferenc\u2019s Poetry. A Critical Introduction to the Issue], author Pawlik-Kopek Aleksandra: ''Dom jako figura artystyczna w poezji Teresy Ferenc. Wst\u0119p do problematyki''.\n*[https://poezja.org/wz/Ferenc_Teresa/ PL Teresa Ferenc], poetry\n*{{cite web |url=https://www.kurierzamojski.pl/teresa-ferenc-ze-wsi-sochy/ |title=Teresa Ferenc ze wsi Sochy |last=Ciurysek |first=Agnieszka |date=13 August 2015 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=Teresa Ferenc from the village of Sochy}}\n*{{cite web |url=https://film.wp.pl/wojna-nie-umiera-nigdy-traumatyczne-wspomnienia-przeszly-z-matki-na-corke-6244246498338433a?src01=f1e45 |title=Wojna nie umiera nigdy. Traumatyczne wspomnienia przesz\u0142y z matki na c\u00f3rk\u0119 |last=Zagalski |first=Jakub |date=23 April 2018 |access-date=12 February 2020 |language=Polish |trans-title=War never dies. Traumatic memories passed from mother to daughter}}\n*{{cite web |url=https://wiadomosci.onet.pl/gdanska-ksiazka-roku-2004/8lrtl |title=Gda\u0144ska Ksi\u0105\u017cka 