a.com/worldcup/matches/round=201/match=1090/ |title=1930 FIFA World Cup Uruguay \u2014 USA 3:0 Belgium |publisher=FIFA|date=2014-07-25 |accessdate=2014-07-30}}</ref>) were played at the same time, as seven players scored, with [[Andr\u00e9 Maschinot]] scoring two goals. The order in which these players are listed reflects the actual elapsed time in the games when their goals were scored.}}\n|-\n| [[Bart McGhee]]\n| {{fb|USA|1912}}\n| {{maybe|'''1'''\u20130}}\n| [[Belgium national football team|Belgium]]\n| align=center| [[1930 FIFA World Cup Group 4#United States vs Belgium|3\u20130]]\n|-\n| [[Marcel Langiller]]\n| {{fb|FRA|1794}}\n| {{maybe|'''2'''\u20130}}\n| [[Mexico national football team|Mexico]]\n| align=center| [[1930 FIFA World Cup Group 1#France vs Mexico|4\u20131]]\n|-\n| [[Andr\u00e9 Maschinot]]\n| {{fb|FRA|1794}}\n| {{maybe|'''3'''\u20130}}\n| [[Mexico national football team|Mexico]]\n| align=center| [[1930 FIFA World Cup Group 1#France vs Mexico|4\u20131]]\n|-\n| [[Tom Florie]]\n| {{fb|USA|1912}}\n| {{maybe|'''2'''\u20130}}\n| [[Belgium national football team|Belgium]]\n| align=center| [[1930 FIFA World Cup Group 4#United States vs Belgium|3\u20130]]\n|-\n| [[Bert Patenaude]]\n| {{fb|USA|1912}}\n| {{maybe|'''3'''\u20130}}\n| [[Belgium national football team|Belgium]]\n| align=center| [[1930 FIFA World Cup Group 4#United States vs Belgium|3\u20130]]\n|-\n| [[Juan Carre\u00f1o]]\n| {{fb|MEX|1916}}\n| {{maybe|'''1'''\u20133}}\n| [[France national football team|France]]\n| align=center| [[1930 FIFA World Cup Group 1#France vs Mexico|1\u20134]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=3| 2\n| [[Andr\u00e9 Maschinot]]\n| {{fb|FRA|1794}}\n| {{success|'''4'''\u20131}}\n| [[Mexico national football team|Mexico]]\n| align=center| [[1930 FIFA World Cup Group 1#France vs Mexico|4\u20131]]\n|\n*[[1930 FIFA World Cup|1930]] vs [[1930 FIFA World Cup Group 1#France vs Mexico|Mexico]]\n|-\n| {{dts|1930|7|16|format=dmy}} \n| [[Carlos Vidal]]\n| {{fb|CHI}}\n| {{maybe|'''3'''\u20130}}